One day, a lion was sleeping peacefully in the jungle until a mouse came by the lion. The mouse tried to run away from the lion bu instead woke up the lion from his nap. The lion woke up and they mouse begged for forgiveness. "Please let me go and some day I will surely repay you," the mouse said. The lion was thinking, "How could a mouse repay me?" and he let the mouse go anyway. A few days later, some hunters came by the jungle and the lion was caught in a huge net. The lion was stuck and unable to make himself free. The lion roared so loudly so that every animal in the jungle can hear him. The mouse heard the lions roar and immediately went to help the lion. The mouse soon found out the the lion was struggling to make himself free.  

